5. Where sale deed has been registered, date of such registration has been considered in Date of Agreement of Sale column in Annexure.
6. For unit number 16, the unit consideration as per agreement to sale is Rs 1,09,35,000. However, as represented by the management, value of sale deed yet to be executed has been agreed at 1,11,85,000 including other charges.
